        <p><MadCap:variable name="Other.Product" /> adds the word to a global dictionary so that it is not flagged as a questionable spelling in the future. The word will also be displayed as a suggestion for future questionable spellings that are very similar. <MadCap:conditionalText MadCap:conditions="Products.Flare">Suggestions can be used by any projects pointing to the dictionary.</MadCap:conditionalText></p>
